In small bowl, combine cilantro, oil, lime juice, garlic, chile powder, cumin and salt. Rub over steaks. Prepare grill to medium heat. Place steaks on grill. Grill, turning once, 7-15 minutes (depending on thickness) or until desired doneness is reached (145 degrees F for medium-rare; 160 degrees F for medium). Remove from grill and season with salt to taste.